## Branches

- main (production branch, releases only)
- dev (active development branch, all PRs merge here first)
- feat/* (feature branches)
- fix/* (bug fix branches)
- chore/* (maintenance tasks, dependencies, etc.)
- etc/*

Branch naming:
- User name
- Issue number
- Conventional commit type
- Associated feature
- Extra tags (e.g. UI, UX, Functionality)
- Description

E.g. `harry/7-feat(auth-ui-ux)/email-and-password-authentication`.

Search for branches associated with the issue before creating one.